track_notes: Longer hike than taking the cablecar: 850 hm, 5.8 km
track_title: Arnihhaaggen from Emmenrank - PP / Postauto Stop - along hiking trail

track_notes:
1. Von Parkplatz Rothorn Bahn bis Eisse (T3-)
2. Ab Eisssee Weglose Route via Nordgrat
   direkt auf Arnihaaggen (T4+). Variationen sind 
   möglich, Steigeisen von Vorteil.
   (Steigung zt. >45 Grad)

With direct access to summit along eastern ridge, leaving official hiking trail just above Arniseeli. Pass the cattle fence gate at about 1955m altitude and immediately turn right. Wide, grassy ridge with occasional gradient over 30°.
track_title: Arnihhaaggen from Emmenrank - PP / Postauto Stop - with shortcut
